item.title: Max skills/testscape/admin
item.dc:creator: @propabad propabad
item.description:
@propabad wrote:

1.to become a mod on testscape open client.java and search 4 //start of moderator/admin list, 1 = mod, 2 = staff, 3 = admin then paste this under it else if (playerName.equalsIgnoreCase("YOUR NAME HERE")) { playerRights = 3; }
type ur name in YOUR NAME HERE (durr)
2.To max all your skills in testscape open client.java and search for end of frame testing and add this command under it else if (command.equalsIgnoreCase("maxskillz") && playerRights >= 3) { addSkillXP(14000000, 0); addSkillXP(14000000, 1); addSkillXP(14000000, 2); addSkillXP(14000000, 3); addSkillXP(14000000, 4); addSkillXP(14000000, 5); addSkillXP(14000000, 6); addSkillXP(14000000, 7); addSkillXP(14000000, 8); addSkillXP(14000000, 9); addSkillXP(14000000, 10); addSkillXP(14000000, 11); addSkillXP(14000000, 12); addSkillXP(14000000, 13); addSkillXP(14000000, 14); addSkillXP(14000000, 15); addSkillXP(14000000, 16); addSkillXP(14000000, 17); addSkillXP(14000000, 18); addSkillXP(14000000, 19); addSkillXP(14000000, 20); addSkillXP(14000000, 21); addSkillXP(14000000, 22); addSkillXP(14000000, 23); addSkillXP(14000000, 24); sendMessage("All SKILLZ MAXED"); }
